- Plugins reload, restart, unload
- Agent reload, restart and unload plugins API/CLI
- lim-agentd /etc/lim/* configs, /etc/lim.d/* per plugin configs
- Lim::CLI Ask(text, cb)/Confirm(text, cb)
- RPC calls should not be able to kill server/client
- Schema mapping RESTful URLs to objects variables
  map => [ '/:parent=>object=>variable[=regex]/:...', ... ]
  map functions:
  - create new objects
  - merge existing objects
- Schema cache settings
